If i use

I will not encounter this problem.

body:
I think this problem is caused by improper decompression.
If I use the default Ubuntu decompression tool to extract, there will be this problem.
If i use 
```bash 
7z x train.7z
```
I will not encounter this problem.
More in-depth reasons have yet to be studied.
Closed.
